Version 1.3.1, 2012-05-20:

	* bugfix in reading GPX files (first line was omitted)

Version 1.3.0, 2011-09-08:

	* change dmin/dmax/hmin/hmax/smin/smax in metadata dialog

Version 1.2.0, 2011-06-23:

	* improved matplotlib integration
